OL,5, A former Edinburgh schoolteacher       
OL,6, accused of sexual abuse by broadcaster 
OL,7, Nicky Campbell and others is fighting  
OL,8, extradition from South Africa.         
OL,10,FThe 83-year-old man - who cannot be    
OL,11,Fnamed for legal reasons - is wanted by 
OL,12,Fthe authorities in the Scottish        
OL,13,Fcapital, where he taught in the 1970s. 
OL,15,FJudges originally approved the UK's    
OL,16,Frequest for his extradition in 2019.   
OL,18,FThe retired teacher lodged an appeal   
OL,19,Fwhich is due to be heard in October.   
